    "org_about":  "The University of Winnipeg in Canada is a dynamic campus that connects people from diverse cultures and nurtures global citizens. It offers high-quality undergraduate and graduate programs including several that are unique in Western Canada, such as Bachelor of Arts in Human Rights and  Master’s in Development Practice with a focus on Indigenous Development. The university is home to more than 600 international students from over 68 countries. With over 5% of the total student population coming from outside Canada, it has many services to ensure that students have a great experience.",
