                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f13b84ed-1270-46f8-a6f5-f30cbcded5f4\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"368\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eThe President\u0026rsquo;s Scholarship for World Leaders is a scholarship program for international students who are enrolling at University of Winnipeg for the first time in undergraduate, graduate, or professional programs. The scholarship is designed to support students with strong academic records, leadership potential, and outstanding community involvement.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
