                                    "header":  "Eligibility criteria",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"58\" data-section-id=\"s2yaf6\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eOpen to international students from all nationalities.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"132\" data-section-id=\"1g40gp4\" data-start=\"59\"\u003eApplicants must have a minimum academic average of 80% or equivalent.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"222\" data-section-id=\"17ve5ah\" data-start=\"133\"\u003eApplicants must be entering University of Winnipeg for the first time.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"324\" data-section-id=\"42iiv0\" data-start=\"223\"\u003eDemonstrated leadership skills and involvement in volunteer or community activities are required.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"384\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-section-id=\"126g6xh\" data-start=\"325\"\u003eFull-time enrollment in the academic program is required.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSee more available \u003ca href=\"https://www.for9a.com/en/opportunity/category/Scholarships/PhD\"\u003ePhd scholarships\u003c/a\u003e on For9a\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSee more available \u003ca href=\"https://www.for9a.com/en/opportunity/category/Competitions-and-Awards\"\u003ecompetition and awards\u003c/a\u003e on For9a\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
